_sText: This is a small map with different styles of bhop that you can practice with. It has mp bhop built into it thanks to a tutorial made by Aoki. I made this map a year ago, just saw it again today then edited it to mp bhop. Please post if you notice any bugs n stuff. Hamster made the tile textures. Thx for viewing, all thats left to do is Download and asses. :)
